name: 11 Birbs Fly Home
description:
Help bring your birb friends home, as you guide them past evil robirbs, and collect seeds for the whole flock to shoot at them with.

All rings will give you a seed, but only the blue rings will get another birb to start following you.

Make sure none of your birbs touch a robirb!

  • WASD/Arrow Keys - Movement
  • Space Bar - Shoot
